quoteText: If any provision of these Terms is found to be unlawful, void, or unenforceable, then that provision will be deemed severable from these Terms and will not affect the validity or enforceability of any remaining provisions.
title: Invalidity of any portion of the Terms of Service does not entail invalidity of its remainder
